{
  "entries": [
    {
      "offset": "0xc8ba1",
      "back_en": "Well, well. Do I have a visitor?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Equivalente."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xc8fc9",
      "back_en": "middle of the day? Outrageous, surely.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xc9155",
      "back_en": "Shall we start with just one cup, then?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xc935a",
      "back_en": "but it's a... nostalgic flavor?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xc937a",
      "back_en": "I've definitely drunk this before, but where...?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Equivalente."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xc93a9",
      "back_en": "What is this?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xc94e1",
      "back_en": "It's nothing, just...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xc94f7",
      "back_en": "I think I've had this somewhere before.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xc99cd",
      "back_en": "but... who is this person anyway?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xc9bd3",
      "back_en": "She reminds me of someone, but who...?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xc9cff",
      "back_en": "I'm Haku.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Sentido preservado."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xc9dd4",
      "back_en": "homeland.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xc9e5c",
      "back_en": "It would be as if a Yamatan parent named their",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xc9e8d",
      "back_en": "child after the Mikado himself. A name beyond",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xc9ef4",
      "back_en": "got my name from a famous person...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xc9f36",
      "back_en": "That girl... gave you that name, did she?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xca27a",
      "back_en": "world.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xca6c1",
      "back_en": "all that's attracted to you is this?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Aceitável dada a ambiguidade."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xca715",
      "back_en": "you in the paths of those you now hold dear...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xca767",
      "back_en": "And a rare one indeed.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xca7ab",
      "back_en": "You all really think...?",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "'Yooouuuu' singular virou 'Vocês' plural."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xca813",
      "back_en": "So, where did I leave off...?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fala arrastada mantida."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xca923",
      "back_en": "That gift you carry is rare indeed.",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "'gift' aqui é 'dom/talento' (cf. 0xca94c), não 'presente'."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xca94c",
      "back_en": "The same gift, I think, as the man you take",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'dom' correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xca98c",
      "back_en": "Only fate could have led you to meet.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xca9b8",
      "back_en": "Yes, you were destined to cross paths",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xca9e8",
      "back_en": "paths...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xcaa1c",
      "back_en": "predetermined by providence.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xcaa78",
      "back_en": "Will you become a conqueror, plunging the world",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'land' como 'mundo', mas coerente no trecho."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xcaaa9",
      "back_en": "into turmoil as you recklessly make your wars?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xcaad8",
      "back_en": "Or... perhaps you will shoulder the burdens of",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xcab09",
      "back_en": "the many, and rules with kindness and love.",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "'governa' (indicativo) quebra o subjuntivo 'carregue'; deveria ser 'governe'."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xcab81",
      "back_en": "It... was soft. Like Kuon's tail.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Equivalente."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xcaba4",
      "back_en": "Oh... That was it. That's... who she reminded",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xcac0f",
      "back_en": "...Was all that just a dream?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xcd87c",
      "back_en": "You know who I am...?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xcd90e",
      "back_en": "nothing.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'nenhuma coisa' literal mas aceitável."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xcd973",
      "back_en": "wavering.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xcd9ab",
      "back_en": "They'll be back.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xcd9bc",
      "back_en": "Yes, I'll leave shortly. But you...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'be away'/'partir' equivalente."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xcda11",
      "back_en": "there are those who live in the shadows...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xcdd41",
      "back_en": "Is it right to let her off unpunished like this?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Sentido preservado."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xcde7f",
      "back_en": "Isn't that... the money stolen in the robbery?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xce12c",
      "back_en": "Ah, how the cold pierces me to the bone,",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'até os ossos' completa o fragmento."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xce183",
      "back_en": "On so cold a night, a drink to warm",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xce1b4",
      "back_en": "the spirit could-- No, thrift. I must be",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xce1e8",
      "back_en": "GAH!? Pain! Whence comes such pain?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Tom arcaico/arrastado mantido."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xce241",
      "back_en": "a blunt object takes him by surprise.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xce265",
      "back_en": "Wh-Who? Who would hold such cruelty and",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xce28f",
      "back_en": "discontent as to throw stones at poor Maroro",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Reordenado mas fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xce2bf",
      "back_en": "at him?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xce2c7",
      "back_en": "...Alas, no voice answers. But what's this!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xce302",
      "back_en": "Wh-Why-- such riches! Fortune beyond compare!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xce32f",
      "back_en": "What a vast chest of coins, in so plain a vessel...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'hoard'/'arca' aceitável."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xce35e",
      "back_en": "Praise the day, blessed coin, for thou art",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xce38b",
      "back_en": "enough to pay Maroro's debts once and",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xce3bb",
      "back_en": "forever!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xce3c3",
      "back_en": "Oh, what an ominous/prescient blessing thou art.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'presagiosa' criativo mas aceitável no registro arcaico."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xce3e8",
      "back_en": "Heaven smiles with kindness upon poor Maroro",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'sweetly'/'com bondade' equivalente."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xce415",
      "back_en": "this day, forsooth!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xce429",
      "back_en": "Whence this blessing comes, so too comes good",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xce459",
      "back_en": "fortune, at last, like a mantle over me",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xce484",
      "back_en": "shoulders.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xce48f",
      "back_en": "Hey, you there. A moment, sir.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xce4e1",
      "back_en": "money from where.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fragmento coerente."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xce4ed",
      "back_en": "Wh-Wherefore dost thou ask? This coin",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xce51a",
      "back_en": "was gifted to me, as befits a gift from",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Passiva/reflexiva equivalente."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xce54b",
      "back_en": "up high.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xce58f",
      "back_en": "Wh-- Wait! This money is",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "Omitiu 'I told thee' ('eu te disse')."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xce5c0",
      "back_en": "the heavens' blessing upon me!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xce650",
      "back_en": "I've done nothing wrong! It's a blessing from",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xce67f",
      "back_en": "the heavens, I say! A blessing...!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xce700",
      "back_en": "sky.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xd0bcc",
      "back_en": "though... Did you guys hear anything vaguely?",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "'lately' (recentemente) virou 'assim de leve' (vagamente)."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xd0d36",
      "back_en": "...Heard anything, eh...?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Equivalente."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xd0f19",
      "back_en": "Oh? Now that's interesting.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xd198a",
      "back_en": "nervous. You're lucky you're just my type.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xd475c",
      "back_en": "And a Kurarin is WHAT, pray tell?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xd6e8f",
      "back_en": "ceiling, as though reflecting on her memories.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xd6f4b",
      "back_en": "my bedside and took care of me...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Correto."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xd6f9a",
      "back_en": "managed to do it properly myself, she was ecstatic.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Fiel."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xd6fef",
      "back_en": "made me take bitter medicine \"for your health.\"",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "'for my health' virou 'para a sua saúde' (your)."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xd704a",
      "back_en": "smiling with longing/nostalgia.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Equivalente."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xd77fa",
      "back_en": "Ack...! It hurts, hurts, it stings--!!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Sentido preservado."
    }
  ],
  "reviewed": 84
}